io.pivotal.rti.protocols

Class ProtocolDetailMap

  • java.lang.Object
    • io.pivotal.rti.protocols.ProtocolDetailMap
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.util.Map<java.lang.String,java.lang.Object>

    public final class ProtocolDetailMap
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.util.Map<java.lang.String,java.lang.Object>
    Custom implementation of Map that allows to store protocol specific details. This map only allows you to store values of type String, Integer, Long, Double, Map and int[]. It also provides a method for concatenating String values without re-writing the previously mapped value to a certain key.
